rows.label: tev910201_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910201_SEL0020
rows.name: Ask who she is.

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0030
rows.name:
Omomo is Omomo. Omomo has retired
from caravan life very long time ago, and
moved to live right here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0040
rows.name:
Caravan pass into hands of Omomo's
littlepon, and Omomo settle here to enjoy
twilight years.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0050
rows.name:
There not much here, but would
welcome friends to feel at home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_JNK0060
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910201_SEL0070
rows.name: Ask about this place.

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0080
rows.name:
Omomo and hubbypon always dreamed of
living in quiet place like this, far away from
everypon else.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0090
rows.name:
Hubbypon now sadly gone to better place,
but Omomo have many fond memories of
living here together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0100
rows.name:
Omomo wish for nothing more
than to live out rest of life here,
where hubbypon sleep in peace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_JNK0110
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910201_SEL0120
rows.name: Ask what she's doing.

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0130
rows.name:
Omomo assembling mementos
of hubbypon. Would like to take all
of them with, if Omomo could...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0140
rows.name:
Will need pots, and ladles, and pans...
Tools for cuisine surely be indispensable.
And also, also, also...![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0150
rows.name:
Meh-meh...
Omomo must pack up in hurry! Would be
so very rude to keep Kylie waiting![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_JNK0160
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910201_SEL0170
rows.name: Ask about Kylie.

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0180
rows.name:
Kylie always been so kind to Omomo.
Omomo is no spring evello anymore...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0190
rows.name:
She pick foodstuffs for Omomo,
and draw water, and run errands
when needed...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0200
rows.name:
Kylie is best friend of Omomo,
but in some ways, she also not
entirely unlike daughterpon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0210
rows.name:
Omomo now understand, family should
stick together. Would never have realized
if not for friends. So thank you, friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_JNK0220
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910201_SEL0230
rows.name: Ask about life in NLA.

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0240
rows.name:
Oho ho ho!
Omomo only recently arrived in NLA,
but life already full of hubbub![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0250
rows.name:
Omomo look after littlepon of littlepon,
make dindins for caravan, all sorts of
business![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0260
rows.name:
But oddly, Omomo not mind so much!
It remind Omomo of youthful days full of
vim and vigor![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_JNK0270
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910201_SEL0280
rows.name: Ask about Kylie.

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0290
rows.name:
Kylie still frequently come
to check up on Omomo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0300
rows.name:
Omomo know she has enough to do
with work for BLADE, but she still come...
Kylie is good littlepon, no question.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0310
rows.name:
Omomo will go with friends, even for
sake of friend Kylie! Omomo will survive!
Because that what best friends do.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0320
rows.name: Cancel

rows.label: tev910201_MSG0330
rows.name: Cancel
